%N A396328 Decimal expansion of Product_{k>=1} exp(-2/k)*(1 + 2/k + 5/(4*k^2)).
%D A396328 H. M. Srivastava and Junesang Choi, Zeta and q-Zeta Functions and Associated Series and Integrals, Elsevier Insights, 2011, p. 367, eq. (21).
%H A396328 Chao-Ping Chen and Junesang Choi, <a href="https://doi.org/10.1080/10652469.2012.693081">Two infinite product formulas with two parameters</a>, Integral Transforms and Special Functions, Vol. 24, No. 5 (2013), pp. 357-363. See p. 358, eq. (1.5).
%H A396328 Chao-Ping Chen and Richard B. Paris, <a href="https://doi.org/10.1080/10652469.2014.885965">Generalizations of two infinite product formulas</a>, Applied Mathematics and Computation, Vol. 25, No. 7 (2014), pp. 547-551. See p. 547, eq. (1.3).
%H A396328 Chao-Ping Chen and Richard B. Paris, <a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.amc.2016.08.003">On the asymptotic expansions of products related to the Wallis, Weierstrass, and Wilf formulas</a>, Applied Mathematics and Computation, Vol. 293 (2017), pp. 30-39. See p. 31, eq. (1.6).
%H A396328 Junesang Choi and Tae Young Seo, <a href="https://www.researchgate.net/publication/266355981">Identities involving series of the Riemann Zeta function</a>, Indian Journal of Pure & Applied Mathematics, Vol. 30, No. 7 (1999), pp. 649-652.
%H A396328 Junesang Choi and Jungseob Lee, <a href="https://doi.org/10.2996/kmj/1050496647">A generalization of Wilf's formula</a>, Kodai Mathematical Journal, Vol. 26, No. 1 (2003), pp. 44-48.
%H A396328 Junesang Choi, <a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.amc.2006.08.091">Some mathematical constants</a>, Applied Mathematics and Computation, Vol. 187, No. 1 (2007), pp. 122-140. See p. 125, eq. (2.23).
%F A396328 Equals (4/5)*exp(-2*gamma)*sinh(Pi/2)/(Pi/2), where gamma is Euler's constant (A001620) (Choi and Seo, 1999).
%e A396328 0.369470683499697314986638952558415503106311745613514...
